<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verificiación de Identidad</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', 'Roboto', serif;
            color: white !important;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            background-image: url('https://viabo.com/production_images/cpay/cpay-bg-3.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            padding-top: 100px
        }

        .content-card {
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 70px auto 40px;
            background-image: url('https://viabo.com/production_images/white_bg.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            border: 2px solid #5C34F5;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: transparent;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 10px
        }

        .card-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px
        }

        .card-header img {
            max-width: 150px
        }

        .card-header h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #297AFA
        }

        .code {
            border: 2px solid #297AFA;
            background-color: #297AFA;
            color: white !important;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .verification-text {
            color: #297AFA;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .additional-text {
            color: #297AFA;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            opacity: 1
        }
    </style>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto">
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="content-card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <img src="https://viabo.com/production_images/cpay/cpay-logo-2x.png" alt="Logo de la empresa">
            <h1>¡Hola,
                {{ name }}!</h1>
            <div class="code">{{ code }}</div>
            <p class="verification-text">Ingresa este código en la plataforma para poder verificar tu cuenta.</p>
            <p class="additional-text">No compartas el código ni el correo con nadie.<br>Si no has solicitado una
